    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "In 1962, North Bellport became the first New York community to face a court case over blockbusting, highlighting early civil rights tensions.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        14
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/North_Bellport%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The Bellport‑Brookhaven Historical Society preserves 19th‑century buildings like the Post‑Crowell House and the Milk House on a 2‑acre campus in the village.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        3,
        4
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
